    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XXXV. Nodalla.\nPreeziga Apfoblichana tahs augſtas Godibas ta jauna Testamanta : 1. Ta poſcha Brihnuwa Leetas : 5. un Labdarrifchanaca ta Mejiafa : 8.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "A Tukſnete nn tukſchas Weetas pahr to preezafees/ un tas Klaijums ithgfinosees / un feedehs ka Rohses.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winna feedeht feedehs/ un lithgfmofees ar Preeku un Gawileſchann/ Libbanus Godiba irr winnai dohta/ tas Glihtums Karmeka un Sarona/ tee redsehs to Godibu ta KUNGA / to\n"
