    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Saffajt tahm tamifhuſcham Sirdim : Effet stipras/ ne bibſteeceſ / Redſi / juhſu Deews/ ta Atreepſchana nahk/ ta Atmakſachana irr Deewa/ wiꞥſch nahks un atpeſtihs juhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
