      "text": "Un tur buhs weens ftatgahts Zetſch/ un weens Zetſch/ kas tas twehts Zetſch taps noſankts/ kas nefchkihts irr tas us to ne ees/ bet wiꞥſch buhs var * treim/ kas us ſcho Zeltu ſtaiga/ tur arridsan tee Nefapracht ne warr maldiht.\n"
